em; font-family: 微软雅黑 !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 51, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp;<img title="556ae94c5f3c9.jpg" alt="556ae94c5f3c9.jpg" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20150604/556fb1795b5e5.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(67, 80, 97); list-style-type: none; font-family: 微软雅黑 !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(67, 80, 97); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑 !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 51, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">头条并不重要，重要的是生活，重要的是音乐。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(67, 80, 97); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑 !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 51, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(67, 80, 97); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑 !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 51, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">河南首场体育场级别的摇滚盛宴，2015年最激情摇滚现场，你只要来听就对了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(67, 80, 97); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑 !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 51, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp;<img title="AP8NETCF00AJ0003.jpg" alt="AP8NETCF00AJ0003.jpg" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20150701/5593bf91aa2f6.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(