n style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1箱配赠品1箱，加赠市场价值168元韩式炒锅1个；或</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">进货</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5箱配赠品5箱，加赠市场价值598元星美电暖器1个。单箱铺市可选择性执行有奖陈列政策（见6.1）。</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">铺货阶段后：</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">第一批进货</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">韓谷辣白菜（1*24）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，进货</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2箱配赠品2箱，加赠市场价值168元韩式炒锅1个；或</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">进货</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">8箱配赠品8箱，加赠市场价值598元星美电暖器1个。</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">第二批进货</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">韓谷辣白菜（1*24）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，进货</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3箱配赠品3箱，加赠市场价值168元韩式炒锅1个；或</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">进货</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">10箱配赠品10箱，加赠市场价值598元星美电暖器1个。</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">之后进货根据市场</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">最新政策执行。</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">以上奖</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">品</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">用于终端铺市</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">或终端特卖会使用</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，使产品迅速</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">形成销售氛围</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">其</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">奖品随货配发</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2.2公司执行箱皮回收政策，按1元/个回收。回收箱皮应保持清洁干净完整，对于污浊破损的箱皮不回收，用于市场堆箱陈列用的箱皮不回收。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">三、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">　袋内投奖</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">支持</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一等奖：韩国5日游，100名</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;二等奖：星美电饭煲1台，10万名</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;三等奖：加1元“再来一袋”韩谷辣白菜方便面1袋(赠品装)，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;100万名。综合中奖率18%，活动日期：即日起-2016年12月31日</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">。备注：“加</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1元”再来一袋，1元做为终端兑奖服务酬劳，由终端收取并获得，公司凭奖卡直接兑换再来一袋。经销商首批进货，前置配备10箱兑奖专用韩谷拉面赠品装及电饭煲5台，用于周转兑奖使用。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">四、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">市场</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">建设</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">支持</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">&nbsp;4.1陈列和堆头特卖支持</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">在终端销售竞争策略上，公司本着“拆箱销售终端利润最大化，整箱销售促销优势最大化”的基本原则，制定以下终端售卖政策：</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">（</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">）堆头促销：（进货</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">10箱</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">/3个底*7个高20箱堆，每月奖励1箱韩谷辣白菜方便面（买一赠一装）,价值120元；</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">进货30箱/</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">5个底*10个高50箱堆</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">每月奖励2箱韩谷辣白菜方便面（买一赠一装），价值240元；</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">进货50箱/</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">10个底*10个高百箱堆，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">每月奖励3箱韩谷辣白菜方便面（买一赠一装），价值360元</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">），时间</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3个月，乡镇市场上限50家，堆头促销协议店必须执行终端特卖会操作政策。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">（2）终端特卖会。原价：120元/箱，现价：100元/箱，买1箱，送1箱，加送168元韩式炒锅1个；买5箱，送5箱，加送598元星美电暖器1个。数量有限，售完为止。活动截止至:见终端海报告知。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">4.2区域广告支持</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">（1）店招支持:</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">公司对于店招广告的投放，按乡镇市场最高店招制作面积不超过100平米，公司只核销喷绘费用，其框架结构部分的费用公司不予以核销，以上核销方式为货补核销，单次100平米以上起核。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">（2）三轮车车体广告支持：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">车体喷绘制作部分以货补核销，每辆三轮车2个月送韩谷辣白菜方便面赠品一箱，乡镇市场投放100辆以内.投放时间六个月。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">（3）核心店店外整体包装支持：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">每个乡镇精选2-3家分销商或乡镇核心卖场，可进行店外整体包装，以货补核销。要求其店内必须执行“百箱促销堆头”特卖会活动。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">（4）配送车体广告支持：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">对于经销商、分销商、及售点送货车辆，提供车体广告喷绘制作费用支持，以货补形式核销。</span></p><p style="text-indent:9px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">（</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">5</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">&nbsp;终端物料支持</span></p><p style="margin-left:48px;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">随货配发ＰＯＰ、围挡、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">推拉贴、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">价格签、帐篷、促销台、服务卡</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">、促销服装、宣传气模</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">等终端物料</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:0"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;五</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">、市场活动支持（韩谷拉面</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">县级市场2-3人搅动活动</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">）</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">（</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">一</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">说明：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">在人员少、资源少的市场作搅动活动，要求活动简单，但声势要大。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">（二）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">地点选择：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">乡镇集市、亮点街道</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">、农贸市场等。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">（</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">三）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">搅动活动组合：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;text-underline:single;font-size:19px">瓶模游街、设点品尝、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;text-underline:single;font-size:19px">现场特卖</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">。（上述可以组合成完整的搅动活动）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">（四）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">所需物料：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">广告运输车一辆（运输及宣传等用），小遮阳篷一个（设点品尝时用），随身扩音器一套（设点品尝及做</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">特卖</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">活动时用），</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">车载</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">扩音器一套（</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">车游小组铺市使用，可选项</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">）</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">品尝台一个（设点品尝），</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">煮面设备一套</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">一次性碗筷若干，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">身穿式气模</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">个</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">、韩式服装</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2套、韩谷寿带2条、面具2个</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">（游街时用）。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">（</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">五）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">具体操作：</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">●&nbsp;事前准备阶段</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">：</span></p><p style="margin-left:24px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1、&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">提前与区域二批商沟通，取得其支持；并进行区域内二批商告知/回访/补货/广宣包装。</span></p><p style="margin-left:24px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2、&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">店外广宣包装：海报（</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2张</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">）、门贴、围挡、条幅、空箱堆箱（</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5个1组，2组为宜</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">）</span></p><p style="margin-left:24px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3、&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">店内形象布置：货架陈列（</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">6个以上的陈列面为宜</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">），促销堆头（进货</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">10箱</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">/3个底*7个高20箱堆，每月奖励1箱韩谷辣白菜方便面,价值120元；</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">进货30箱/</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">5个底*10个高50箱堆</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">每月奖励2箱韩谷辣白菜方便面，价值240元；</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">进货50箱/</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">10个底*10个高百箱堆，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-style:italic;font-size:19px">每月奖励3箱韩谷辣白菜方便面，价值360元</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">）。</span></p><p style="margin-left:24px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">4、&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">设备和物料准备。</span></p><p style="margin-left:24px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5、&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">搅动程序设置和演练。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">●&nbsp;事中开展阶段</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px">：</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">第一项：游街造势：约1小时时间（2-3个回合）；</span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">瓶模游街宣传，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">个人穿着瓶模</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">、</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2个着韩式服装组成三人小队</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">走街造势，可手举</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">广告牌</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">，（适用于集市，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">铺市前终端预热，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">氛围较好）。</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">其中</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">人散发宣传品，引领口号</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">(韩国风味，韩谷拉面)</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">等。</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">注意着韩式服装人员必须佩戴韩谷寿带和面具。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">第二项：设点品尝：约2个小时左右（加</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">特卖</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">时间）；</span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">基础活动：十字路口摆设小遮阳篷，&nbsp;摆设品尝台，一人身带随身扩音器进行推介宣传。其他两个人辅助。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">第三项：</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">现场特卖</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">：</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;现场做1个百箱产品促销堆和1个百箱套装锅促销品展示堆，布置主题促销活动现场，营造现场活动气氛（可以派发韩谷气球）。扬声品滚动播放促销内容：韩国风味，韩谷拉面，厂家直供，现场特卖。买1箱，送1箱，加送168元精品炒锅1个；买5箱，送5箱，加送598元电暖器1个。数量有限，售完为止。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">●&nbsp;事后跟进事项：</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;趁热展开铺市、开新店活动、终端压仓活动。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span