	(209, 4, 6775, '电工圆铝杆加工项目', '电工圆铝杆生产加工项目是以国标铝锭和废铝或铝液为原料，经过高炉融化、精炼、浇铸等工序，生产出符合国标要求的电工圆铝杆的生产项目。', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:24px;font-family:宋体">电工圆铝杆生产加工项目介绍</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="line-height:150%">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left:112px;line-height: 200%"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:200%">一、<span style="font-weight: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">项目基本情况</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">电工圆铝杆生产加工项目是以国标铝锭和废铝为原料，经过高炉融化、精炼、浇铸等工序，生产出符合国标要求的电工圆铝杆的生产项目。</span></p><p style="margin-left:112px;line-height: 200%"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:200%">二、<span style="font-weight: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">生产工艺和流程</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">上料</span>----<span style="font-family:宋体">高炉熔炼</span>-----<span style="font-family:宋体">保温炉精炼</span>-----<span style="font-family:宋体">浇铸</span>-------<span style="font-family:宋体">连铸连铸</span>------<span style="font-family:宋体">收线</span>------<span style="font-family:宋体">发货</span></p><p style="margin-left:112px;line-height: 200%"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:200%">三、<span style="font-weight: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">产品定价、类型和经营模式</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">原材料和产品销售均是现款交易。原材料需预付款；产品销售部分预收款，部分货到付款。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">原材料定价模式：每个交易日铝长江现货均价上浮或下浮固定金额。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">产品销售定价模式：每个交易日铝长江现货均价</span>+<span style="font-family:宋体">加工费</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">产品销售均是订单式生产，无库存。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">本项目产品主要分两种</span>: <span style="font-family:宋体">普通电工圆铝杆和合金杆，加工费为每吨</span>580-1800<span style="font-family:宋体">元。</span></p><p style="margin-left:112px;line-height: 200%"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:200%">四、<span style="font-weight: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">单条生产线产量和需要流资</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">一条生产线白班生产日均产量</span>70<span style="font-family:宋体">吨，月保守产量</span>2000<span style="font-family:宋体">吨。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">为保证连续生产，每天需采购两车</span>80<span style="font-family:宋体">吨，按铝价高点每吨</span>14000<span style="font-family:宋体">元约需</span>130<span style="font-family: 宋体">万元，按现铝价每吨</span>10700<span style="font-family:宋体">元需</span>81<span style="font-family:宋体">万元。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">故需预备三日流资约</span>250-400<span style="font-family:宋体">万元可保证连续生产。</span></p><p style="margin-left:112px;line-height: 200%"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:200%">五、<span style="font-weight: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height: 200%;font-family:宋体">市场和客户情况</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">我们现有客户区域为湖北、湖南、江西、河南、福建、江苏和广东，主要是大型电缆生产厂家。</span><