amily:宋体">万元。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-family:宋体">按投入</span>400<span style="font-family:宋体">万元测算，月收益率</span>5%<span style="font-family:宋体">，年收益率</span>60%<span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></p><p><br/></p>', 30, 4000000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1456110602, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201602/56ca7b26da103.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 1, 0, 11, 149, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
