	(240, 3, 6851, '省级非物质文化遗产——郑家老粉坊', '安阳全盛郑家老粉坊出品，河南非物质文化遗产，300年绿豆粉皮生产历史！', '<p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(204, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">100%纯正绿豆粉皮</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(204, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">安阳全盛郑家老粉坊出品</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(204, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">河南非物质文化遗产</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(204, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">300年绿豆粉皮生产历史</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><img width="806" height="159" title="绿豆1225.png" style="width: 769px; height: 151px;" alt="绿豆1225.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a3965d3c2.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(56, 118, 29); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;"><img width="703" height="320" title="绿豆1349.png" style="width: 764px; height: 332px;" alt="绿豆1349.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a3b040d1a.png"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(56, 118, 29); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;"><img width="700" height="341" title="绿豆1474.png" style="width: 767px; height: 347px;" alt="绿豆1474.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a3dc6c0a2.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img width="701" height="339" title="绿豆1597.png" style="width: 762px; height: 347px;" alt="绿豆1597.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a3f49bc08.png"/></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(56, 118, 29); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">目前网上卖绿豆粉皮的很多，但卖纯绿豆粉皮的卖家不到6家。10元8元一斤的绿豆粉皮都是挂羊头卖狗肉。大家可以计算一下，目前的绿豆价格是8元至10元一斤，一斤绿豆可以出150克到200克绿豆淀粉，一斤绿豆淀粉可以出一斤绿豆粉皮干货，这样算来，一斤纯绿豆粉皮所消耗的绿豆就在20元左右。呵呵，那些10元8元一斤的号称纯绿豆粉皮是怎么做出来的。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆1890.png" alt="绿豆1890.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a4530a6bc.png"/></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 229, 153); color: rgb(39, 78, 19); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 36px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">本次<a href="http://www.zczyw.com" target="_self" title="众筹" style="font-size: 36px; text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: rgb(39, 78, 19); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 36px; background: rgb(255, 229, 153);">众筹</span></a>的粉皮为安阳全盛郑家老粉坊手工制作的100%纯绿豆粉皮，口感劲道爽口，不含任何添加剂。不是那些10元8元一斤的粉皮。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 36px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline;">下面图片均有我家实图拍摄</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆11089.png" alt="绿豆11089.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a4bc6c2df.png"/></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 229, 153); color: rgb(39, 78, 19); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 36px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">我家绿豆粉皮一斤大约9张左右，薄厚适中，非常合适家庭食用。有些绿豆粉皮一斤可达到20张左右的超薄粉皮，这种粉皮为机器制作，饭店使用较多。我家的手工粉皮无法做出这样薄的粉皮。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆11300.png" alt="绿豆11300.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a55c394e5.png"/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: left; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(39, 78, 19); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">纯绿豆粉皮是粉皮中的极品。纯绿豆粉皮呈现乳白色或略带蛋青色,如果粉皮是绿色,则是掺了色素制做的。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆11654.png" alt="绿豆11654.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a59a8c05a.png"/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: left; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(39, 78, 19); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">纯绿豆粉皮用手有一定的硬度和弹性,用手拉时有韧性,如掺了红薯淀粉的假粉皮与真的相比,色泽发暗,弹性、韧性都较差。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(39, 78, 19); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">纯绿豆粉皮吃在嘴里不面、不软、不糟,有口劲。而掺了土豆、玉米淀粉的粉皮,外观与绿豆粉皮虽差不多,但硬度大、没有弹性,软糟或发面。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆11843.png" alt="绿豆11843.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a5fb74c08.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆11967.png" alt="绿豆11967.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a6234130e.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆12118.png" alt="绿豆12118.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a6a0073a0.png"/></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(56, 118, 29); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">我们的包装。我们是自行包装的，一袋净含量是250克。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆12419.png" alt="绿豆12419.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a6ca5e584.png"/></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(246, 178, 107); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">纯绿豆粉皮泡发秘笈：</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(246, 178, 107); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">1：将粉皮放入温水或者热水泡软；</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(246, 178, 107); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">2：把泡软的粉皮放入沸水中慢煮8分钟左右（绿豆粉皮泡发量大，加水要足。）</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(246, 178, 107); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">3：把沸水关火，粉皮继续在热水中泡发8分钟左右（此时，粉皮应该和水同色）</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(246, 178, 107); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">4：把粉皮取出，投入冷水中，备用。</span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 0px;"><span style="background: rgb(246, 178, 107); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">大部分人吃粉皮菜，外形柔软而口感生硬，放入很多调料却不出味，大多是泡发不到的原因。好东西没有吃出好感觉，可惜啊！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img title="绿豆12419.png" alt="绿豆12419.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a761204e7.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆12543.png" alt="绿豆12543.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a7ab1f417.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img title="绿豆12692.png" alt="绿豆12692.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a8639b089.png"/><img title="绿豆13077.png" alt="绿豆13077.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a87f620d8.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img width="752" height="540" title="绿豆13254.png" style="width: 762px; height: 540px;" alt="绿豆13254.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a8987f5f7.png"/><img width="751" height="531" title="绿豆13378.png" style="width: 832px; height: 551px;" alt="绿豆13378.png" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160504/5729a8db52cd4.png"/></p>', 90, 10000.00, 4, 58, 11500.00, 1462348026, 1462348800, 1470240000, '/data/upload/201605/5729a2c899bc2.png', '\' \'', '', 1, 1, 0, 11, 152, ' 郑家老粉坊——河南省省级非物质文化遗产', '郑家米粉,郑家米粉众筹', '安阳全盛郑家老粉坊出品，河南非物质文化遗产，300年绿豆粉皮生产历史！', 0, 6, 8, 0),
