utospace:ideograph-other"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:楷体_GB2312">三心一如</span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:楷体_GB2312">空觉极圆</span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:楷体_GB2312">是圆觉体</span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:楷体_GB2312">具八功德</span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:宋体">目</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family: 宋体">录</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">大同心印</span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">序</span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">上卷</span> <span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">大同法要</span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">中卷</span> <span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:#333333">法要串讲</span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">下卷</span> <span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:#333333">经世致用</span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">后记</span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:宋体">序</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style="text-indent:47px;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">当今世界，虽然人间小灾不断，但科学昌明，信息广通，生产力极大解放，生产资料亦极大丰富，人民皆求民主自由平等解放，处处暗藏世界大同之象。故吾集十数载之证悟，以此《明学》传世。寄希望于有睹此书而心存世界大同理想者，依法参悟修持，见性明心，成就自心净土。或可于心中勒天道变异于顷刻，纠因果错乱于当下，销人间灾劫于未发，化娑婆世界为大同。修习明学者，当发大愿立大心，以三世诸佛菩萨为师，弥陀为父，极乐为母，众生为兄弟姐妹，誓化娑婆秽土为净土大同，是为入大同侠圣境界。则无论今世成功与否，必定成就世出世间最胜功德，必定临终往生极乐净土，必定未来成佛作祖。若是妄语，吾愿堕无间地狱，永不出离。当知遇此法者，皆是福慧深厚；德浅福薄之人，实难觅此书踪迹，况夫学乎！故我得此法不易，汝遇此法不易，遇此法而真发心修学者，更为不易。通读此书一遍者，必积一劫褔慧功德；通读三遍以上者，必定心开悟解；悟后起修者，所积智慧福德，语言算数所不能譬喻；修而有成者，或内圣而外侠，或内侠而外圣，或外凡而内侠圣，境界之深远，世智辨聪者难以测量。吾数易文稿，最终必待自心印证无咎，方才放出。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">修行无止境，吾所悟成就自心大同净土之法，本人尚未全修全得全证。然得书之人，切不可以为著书者尚未全证而轻慢此书，草草阅之而放下。何故？明学大同之法，本为法界众生，全体起修全体证解之道，设若只归于一人得道，则为小同。故参学者越多，法脉愈胜，相互参照，互察互纠，共做照明。不可存</span><span style="font-size:19px">“</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">一人得道，鸡犬升天</span><span style="font-size:19px">”</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">之想，落人后也！</span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">修明学者，首当明了</span><span style="font-size:19px">“</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">人法二无我为大，万法一如为同</span><span style="font-size:19px">”</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体">，是谓大同法印。无论初学、中修、末了，皆当依此法印循序渐进，融会贯通。依大同法要，一心念佛持咒，勤行勒道之法，降伏自心变异之道，了却颠倒错乱因缘。生时依定慧之力经世致用实现自心大同境界，临终往生极乐觉悟菩提，或开天辟地另造净土，则大同之密尽矣！</span></p><p style="text-align:right;text-autospace:ideograph-other"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:楷体_GB2312">——叶勒安记于九泉含笑宅</span></p><h1 label="标题居中" style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: center; margin: 0px 0px 20px;"><br/></h1>', 60, 30000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1471534406, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201608/57b5d4ac88ea5.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 1, 0, 11, 156, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
