	(341, 2, 34081, '主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！', '邀请志同道合的人一起来到石牛寨国家地质公园4A级景区，一起把皇宫洒店建设成一个温馨的大家庭。', '<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">我的身世介绍</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我出生在湖南省平江县石牛寨国家地质公园4A级旅游景区附近，离景区二公里左右，位置环境十分优越，是恩人一手把我建起来的，恩人准备把我打造成皇宫酒店，帮我穿上古代皇宫一样的衣服，要我成为全国都独一无二的特色酒店。</p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca311060ba.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f60c5c9042f1a_t4_2000x1500_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 503px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">我的母亲石牛寨国家地质公园介绍</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我的母亲叫石牛寨国家地质公园，属于国家级AAAA级景区，现正筹建5A，每年大约有200万游客，位于湘、鄂、赣边界的平江县石牛寨镇（原大坪乡）境内，有一座方圆10余平方公里的古军事要地石牛寨，它是由怪石、奇峰、石洞组成的丹霞石的世界，鬼斧神工，千姿百态，美不胜收。寨内景点众多，仅叫得出名的景点概括下来就有“一牛二龟三关险，四桥五寨六线天，七奇石八寺庙，百零八崖景无边”等。各景点以奇险著称，尤为罕见的是保存完好的2000多米古城墙，享有“天下第一寨”之美誉。</p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca255d5ef1.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f60ce4efdff1a_t4_750x500_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 447px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca2560b500.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f6117aab1131a_t4_670x502_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 502px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca2567fdc4.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f61199599971a_t4_1584x954_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 404px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p class="xqLeftTitle_p" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; height: 22px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);"><br/></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">玻璃桥景区</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2014年10月1日，目前国内跨度大、高度最高的“玻璃桥”在湖南岳阳平江石牛寨景区开通并投入使用，来自全国各地的游客来此体验“心跳之旅”。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">石牛寨旅游区（国家级AAAA级景区）的玻璃桥桥长300米、垂直高度达到180米，悬于海拔540多米高的大矛寨与美人峰之间，两峰崖壁陡直，中间裂谷横穿，走在桥面彷如云中漫步。游客体验凌空而行的同时，还能游览碧水丹霞景区、兵寨文化体验区、丹霞石佛观光区，领略大自然百里丹霞的壮美。</p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca256d73e1.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f611ea0ab9b1a_t4_960x540_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 377px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca2572cd8e.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f611f1de6611a_t4_800x533_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 446px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">恩人为什么要把我寄养？</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我的恩人为了把我养大，花了很多的钱，我现在框架已经基本成型了，恩人为了让我穿的更漂亮，培养一个更有用的人，所以才忍痛割爱的把我寄养给其它的主人，在这十年的寄养里，主人一定要对我关心，我一定会懂得知恩仇报的。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca29d1d4e2.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f60c5c9042f1a_t4_2000x1500_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 503px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca273a97f3.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/16/57f61202288011a_t4_750x500_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 447px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p class="xqLeftTitle_p" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; height: 22px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);"><br/></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">我的恩人是个怎样的人？</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我的恩人叫樊后来，都说后来居上，所以我的名言是：后来居上，成就你我。已经36岁啦，从走出校园后，和很多的人一样，来到了繁华的大都市打拼，有过几年的酒店管理经验，在09年时和几个合伙人一起创办了中国国际剧本网，是非常成功的，现在每个股东每年都可以分到上百万的利润，这也是第一次创业，经过这些年的发展，人也到了中年，刚好家乡旅游发生了很大的变化，从一个没人问津的小地方现在变成了全国著名的旅游胜地，于是在2012年就开始了在家乡发展的想法，经过几年在全国各地考察总结的经验，于去年在当地政府的支持下，终于拿到了地皮，开始了酒店的建设。</p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca2740e5e6.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/08/11/57f863e2943cb1a_t4_1024x768_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 503px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p class="xqLeftTitle_p" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; height: 22px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);"><br/></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">我的优点</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">恩人在找我的时候就考虑到因为离景区太近的话会让很多游客顾忌，现在游客都有这种心态，在景区周围的东西不是价格高就是宰客，如果离景区太远就失去了开景区酒店的意义，所以就选在离景区二公里不远不近的地方刚好选择了我，所以我很感谢恩人，到景区只需几分钟的车程，并且可以看到景区。我离省道只有90米，这样完美的解决了离马路太近会太吵、飞尘太多的问题，但在马路上又直接可以看到我，交通十分便利，离高速公路也只有500米左右，在高速路上都可以看到我的，再一个我是市级的一个示范点，政府十分重视，专门给我们定位开农家乐酒店的，将重点打造成一个民宿村。</p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca274b2e77.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/17/57f6182f0db7d1a_t4_3200x2400_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 503px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca27532b99.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/17/57f618436c6c51a_t4_3200x2400_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 503px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p class="xqLeftTitle_p" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; height: 22px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);"><br/></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">我的详细分析</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我的身高体重：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">总面积约三亩左右，建筑面积约1800平方，分为四层，第一层是餐厅，第二三层是住宿，第四层是员工宿舍，客房三十间，餐厅可同时融入400人以上就餐，其中室内同时可融入200人左右，室外同时可融入200人以上，有大型停车场。</p><p><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">恩人对我的定位：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">定位为中高档酒店，以精致高品位的“皇宫景区”为项目主体，提供集住宿、餐饮、旅游、表演及休闲娱乐为一体的旅游体验。</p><p><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2、主要目标人群分析</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">适合各种旅游人群。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">消费目的：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">主要以别人来观看皇宫景点和穿皇帝古装衣服拍照及一些创意来拉动餐饮、住宿、特产和景区产品消费。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">人群来源：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">现在是自驾游为主，特别是现在人的心理，一般去一个地方都会在网上先查好攻略，只要去这个地方旅游的人都会打听附近的景点，都会去玩，所以只要是来旅游的人一般都会到皇宫景区游玩。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">需求特点：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">别人到皇宫景区来玩，很多都会选择在这里就餐，因为在这里可以免费看节目，免费拍照，免费参加活动等等一系列的好玩的东西，让他比去石牛寨更有趣。</p><p><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3、景区周边宾馆以农家乐居多，在硬件设施上与皇宫酒店差距较大。镇上宾馆大多是由民宅改造而成，空间狭窄，床位少，接待量有限，但他们的优点是价格低，成本低。每到旅游旺季一房难求，景区甚至全国都没有一家以皇宫这样为主题的酒店，让人感觉到特别新鲜，具有独一无二的竞争性。</p><p><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">商业模式：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1、基于以上的市场分析，将定位为以中国古代皇宫文化为主题的度假酒店。这个市场领域目前是空白。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2、特色元素的酒店很多，唯独没有以朝代皇宫为主题的装修风格。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3、皇宫景区，目前湖南，湖北，江西三省主要客源中都没有这种景点，大大吸引游客的目光，每个人都想当一次皇帝，在这就可以实现，在全国等地考察了一些与皇宫有关的景区，最能吸引人的就是皇帝宝座这块，但我发现很多的这个景点都是收费的，但我们免费，所以本酒店就抓住了大部份人的心理精心设计的。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4、只要在酒店定房消费的，就可以免费领圣旨一张，要多张以50元的价格出售，这个圣旨特别有纪念收藏价值，不说其它的，大多数人都会冲着这个来消费，因为圣旨的内容就特别有意义，值的一辈子珍藏和回忆。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5、每天有表演，如: 接派圣旨表演，篝火晚会表演，抽奖活动等，让游客体验真正身在皇宫那种君臣的感觉。</p><p><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">皇宫酒店经营特色：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1、建立石牛寨旅游网shiniuzhai.wang 石牛寨皇宫酒店shiniuzhai.cn 石牛寨皇宫景区shiniuzhai.com.cn网站。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2、和旅游网站和旅行社建立合作。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3、免费提供红军服装，古装衣服，自行车出租。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4、本店所有员工都穿古装衣服。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5、免费穿皇帝，格格，古装衣服在皇帝宝座拍照。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">6、晚上搞古装篝火晚会，你可能参与的篝火晚会不计其数，但我相信您一定没有见过几十个人都穿皇帝和格格衣服一起参加篝火晚会的，这种场面非常壮观，非常有意义。</p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161011/57fca27596a91.jpg" alt="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" title="主人，我好可怜哦，快来收养我吧！ (酒店,饭店,宾馆)" data-src="http://zcr6.ncfstatic.com/attachment/201610/06/17/57f616f2dc3dd1a_t4_2000x1500_thumb_670x0.jpg" class="lazy1 go" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: top; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; max-width: 100%; display: block; height: 503px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; width: 670px; opacity: 1 !important; background: url(http://zcs5.ncfstatic.com/v3/static/images/lazy1.png?v=1476096052) no-repeat rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p class="xqLeftTitle_p" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: 26px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; height: 22px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);"><br/></p><h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 12px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 41px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; height: 41px; border: 3px solid rgb(241, 241, 241); color: rgb(80, 171, 242); min-width: 80px;">为什么我需要你的支持及资金用途？</h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0p