	(371, 3, 37321, '现摘新鲜原生态水果，来自世界橙乡的赣南脐橙，诚邀您品尝', '赣南脐橙，是江西省赣州市的特产，中国国家地理标志产品，果大形正，橙红鲜艳，光洁美观，肉质脆嫩、化渣，风味浓甜芳香，热情淳朴的客家人诚邀您品尝。', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">秋天，是赣南脐橙收获的季节；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">历经一年的辛劳，赣南脐橙硕果累累；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">田间地头，一片金黄；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">金果压枝，灿若群星；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">我是赣南脐橙果农，我也是大自然的搬动工</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161108/5821a98a2baf6.jpg" style="" title="TB2f0Sca.5O.eBjSZFxXXaaJFXa_!!2937051531.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161108/5821a98abd262.jpg" style="" title="TB2RPyga9iK.eBjSZFsXXbxZpXa_!!2937051531.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161108/5821a9e0733e6.jpg" title="TB2Q9aja8aM.eBjSZFMXXcypVXa_!!2937051531.jpg" alt="TB2Q9aja8aM.eBjSZFMXXcypVXa_!!2937051531.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161108/5821aa9e28e0c.jpg" title="89815af5df964c93b5698df128c21647.jpg" alt="89815af5df964c93b5698df128c21647.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161108/5821a98cefdb4.jpg" style="" title="TB2ygKqaH5K.eBjy0FfXXbApVXa_!!2937051531.jpg"/></p><p style=