	(383, 3, 38534, '双12 提前优惠全场8折 蟹肉上席百味淡', '太湖清水大闸蟹\r\n\r\n     又称湖蟹，学称螯蟹。《太湖备考》上有“出太湖者，大而色黄、壳坚，胜于他产，冬日益肥美，谓之十月雄”的记载，以肉嫩味美、黄多膏丰著称，为太湖名贵水产之一。', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><img alt="轻松筹" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161201/583f88be895d3.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: auto !important; max-width: 100%;"/><span style="font-size:16px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;">太湖是一个天然的湖泊，是中国的四大淡水湖之一。江南一直被人们称为是鱼米之乡，而太湖流域更是标准的鱼米之乡。太湖宽广无比，虽然没有大海那么浩瀚，但有时候在太湖中也有那种一望无际的感觉。太湖湖水洁净，正是这些优质的水，养育了一代代的人，全国8%的人士靠太湖水养育的，太湖流域占3%的面积，却创造了全国四分之一的财富，好水养好人。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:16px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;">太湖蟹是我国有名的淡水蟹之一。肉质鲜嫩，味美，黄多脂肥，历来被誉为蟹中之珍品。“九月团脐十月尖”就是说，九月要吃雌蟹（寒露以后），十月要选雄蟹（立冬左右），这时，他们的营养价值成分极为丰富。</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;"><span style="font-size:16px;box-sizing: border-box;">太湖蟹有生殖回游的特性，在江海交界处繁殖，淡水中生长育肥，太湖蟹体形大，青背白肚，黄毛金钩，完全可与阳澄湖大闸蟹媲美。太湖蟹一般净重200-250克左右，肉质细腻，营养丰富，含有丰富的蛋白质、脂肪、钙、磷、铁、维生素A、核黄素、硫胺素等。药用价值甚高，能散淤血，舒筋接骨，解毒，蟹爪还有催产下胎之功能。 　　“秋尽江南蟹正肥”。中秋以后，太湖螃蟹性腺成熟，正是赏菊食蟹的好时节，历来吃蟹有“九雌十雄”的习惯。这时的太湖螃蟹，油足肉紧，煮熟后雌的壳内呈桔红色的“蟹黄”，雄的壳内呈半透明乳白色的“蟹膏”。据清《清嘉录》描述：太湖地区有炸蟹习俗。“湖蟹乘潮上簖，渔者捕得之，担入城市，居人买以相馈贶，或宴客佐酒。有九雌十雄之曰，谓九月团脐佳，十月尖脐佳也”。“蟹味上桌百味淡”，即指吃过蟹后再吃任何其它菜肴，便会觉得如同嚼蜡一般淡而无味。 　　吃太湖蟹既是品尝佳味，又是一种艺术享受，历代文人为之吟诗、著文、绘画甚多。曹雪芹在《红楼梦》中，描写大观园内食蟹吟诗的热闹情景：“持螯更喜桂阴凉，泼醋捣姜兴欲狂”，逼真地道出了吃蟹的最好季节和方法。太湖大闸蟹为地理标志保护产品。</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:18px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;">好水养好蟹</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><img alt="轻松筹" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161201/583f88bee7587.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: auto !important; max-width: 100%;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><img alt="轻松筹" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161201/583f88bf72633.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: auto !important; max-width: 100%;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:16px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;">大约在每年2、3月份，蟹农会将来自长江水域的蟹苗投放到崇明岛蟹苗基地放养，然后在清明前再把蟹苗接回到阳澄湖、太湖等养殖基地，选蟹苗要把握脚长、毛黄、背青、肚白、活力强这五大基本原。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size:16px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;">之所以选择阳澄湖和太湖作为养殖基地，是因为这里有着大闸蟹生长的天然优势。首先，水位要保持在1.5-2米之间。其次，水温要保持在8℃左右。且水质要清澈，据了解，阳澄湖与太湖是上海等地区市民的直饮水。还有一点就是，在养殖水域附近需要有自然生长茂盛的水草，为养殖区域营造一个完整的生态链，以保证大闸蟹有一个自然、平衡的生长环境。海葫芦等海生植物茂密的漂浮在养殖区域，且有若干白鹭等鸟类栖息在此，一派和谐、美好的生态环境。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><img alt="轻松筹" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161201/583f88bfc1474.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: auto !important; max-width: 100%;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><img alt="轻松筹" src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20161201/583f88bff2813.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: auto !important; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hira