	(413, 3, 39012, ' 药食同源减肥壮阳，滋补养颜降三高，被称为东洋参的黄金牛蒡茶', '营养学家认为牛蒡是中药也是蔬菜营养价值很高而牛蒡茶是以中草药牛蒡根为原料的纯天然茶品，特别适用人群便秘、糖尿病、高血脂及亚健康人群。', '<p><span style="font-weight: 600; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">首先感谢众筹中原平台给予我这个做电商的机会。让农民们的产物能够以最实惠的价格和品质把绿色和健康直接送到每个支持者朋友的手里。这是我最高兴的事情，也更是朋友们最高兴的事情！</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">牛蒡茶是以中草药牛蒡根为原料的茶品，牛蒡茶选用优质牛蒡根，其色泽金黄、香味宜人，是老幼四季皆宜的营养饮品。&nbsp;牛蒡为苍山的主要栽培模式之一。被国家标准委确定为“无公害农产品”，主要出口日本、韩国、美国、台湾等国家和地区，苍山县被国家特产委命名为“中国牛蒡之乡”、被誉为山东的“洋菜园”。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30.6px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7e834d7fb2.jpg" title="q1.jpg" alt="q1.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">生态种植，爱上健康，恋上牛蒡，万亩牛蒡种植基地。</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7e892c9b71.jpg" title="q2.jpg" alt="q2.jpg"/><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7e8a6561d2.jpg" title="q3.jpg" alt="q3.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如今越来越多的茶叶都被打了农药，猪肉不敢吃、牛奶不敢喝！我们还敢相信什么？就在这里我们敢百分百的保证牛蒡茶是绿色的！天然的！想造假想打农药都不行。</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7e8ddad3b4.jpg" title="11.jpg" alt="11.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">世界各国誉为21世纪最具营养价值的健康食补品--黄金牛蒡；</span><span style="font-size: large; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">产地苍山！地下1.5米无农药污染！滋补养颜&nbsp;滋补养颜降三高！</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">牛蒡的根在1.5米的地底下，</span>不会受到农药的污染，不管你信不信！反正我信了！有图有真相，</span><span style="font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">而且我们的牛蒡茶产于“牛蒡之乡”苍山，</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color:#880000;box-sizing: border-box;">产地和原料直接决定了牛蒡茶的品质，选用来自“</span><span style="color:#0000ff;box-sizing: border-box;">中国牛蒡之乡”山东苍山的牛蒡是最好的</span><span style="color:#880000;box-sizing: border-box;">，因为那里特别的土壤以及新鲜干净的空气、水分培育出的牛蒡营养丰富、生命力强，是中国牛蒡的原产地和出口首选地！</span></span></span></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7eaf086a9d.jpg" title="img.jpg" alt="img.jpg"/></p><p><span style="font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: large; line-height: 32.4px; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">牛蒡茶的功效：</strong></span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">提高免疫力、增强体力、减肥养颜、排毒通便、防癌抗癌、平衡体质、疏风散热、解毒消肿、防范文明病、去脂助消化、降低胆固醇、改善人体新陈代谢可平衡血压、调节血糖、血脂、补血补钙、滋阴壮阳、补肾益气健脾开胃对高血压、糖尿病、类风湿、性机能减退、肥胖症、内外痔等有显著的改善效果。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">国家权威药典中把牛蒡的药理作用概括为</span></strong><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">三个方面：</strong></span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;">第一有促进生长作用</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;">第二有抑制肿瘤生长的物质</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px;">第三有抗菌和抗真菌作用。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 24px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">适用人群便秘、糖尿病、高血脂及亚健康人群。</span><br/></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7ecb786a94.jpg" title="img (1).jpg" alt="img (1).jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">牛蒡茶的冲泡方法：</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size: 18px;">具体做法</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 热饮每次5-8克备注7到8片便秘者、减肥者可酌情增加。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 用开水冲泡2-3分钟即可饮用可反复冲泡多次也可以配以冰糖、红枣、洋参冲泡效果更佳还可以放少许蜂蜜预防上火</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 26px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30.6px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">开水冲泡，几分钟后，汤色金黄透亮泛红色，轻轻一嗅，牛蒡味香浓怡人，入口柔滑，舒爽醇香，自然浓郁，耐冲泡。</span></span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7ebe43cc48.jpg" title="q8.jpg" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7ebe43d891.jpg" style="" title="q7.jpg"/></p><p><span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30.6px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">泡过的牛蒡片底红棕透亮，片剂饱满，精挑细选，切片均匀，余香怡人。</span></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7ebe43fd42.jpg" style="" title="q9.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7ebe4820f7.jpg" style="" title="q10.jpg"/></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 24px;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">牛蒡茶的注意事项</strong></span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size: 18px;">⒈牛蒡茶具有润肠通便的效果初饮者可能出现排便功能增强不是水泻现象。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ⒉专家建议在饮用牛蒡茶的时候不要吃辛辣的食物不要熬夜以防出现上火。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ⒊牛蒡茶夏季保存应采取防潮措施。食用时不必再清洗以防营养流失。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ⒋因牛蒡茶有助于辅助稳定降低高血压建议低血压患者间歇饮用。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ⒌不与其它茶混饮泡发的茶片最后食掉最佳。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ⒍坚持饮用一个月就会有明显效果。</span></p><p style="font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, arial; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-indent: 32px; font-size: medium; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7.牛蒡茶不宜过浓过浓容易引起上火在泡 制的时候可以适当的加入一些蜂蜜这样就不会上火了!</span></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7edbbd9954.jpg" title="1108252572_378768442_.jpg" alt="1108252572_378768442_.jpg"/><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170218/58a7eeec8ca4b.jpg" title="20_副本.jpg" alt="20_副本.jpg"/></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30.6px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为感谢新老朋友的支持与厚爱，凡是购买1500克（3斤）的朋友均送同款500克（1斤），详情请参见产品回报。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30.6px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(136, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;">配送与</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">售后</span><span style="font-weight: 600; font-size: x-large; color: rgb(136, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;">：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; padding-bottom: 20px; font-family: &#39;Lanti