	(467, 9, 39134, '鸵鸟主题餐厅', '鸵鸟主题餐厅目前在很多城市尚属空白，因此其发展前景非常好。鸵鸟这种动物见过的人很多，但吃过的人很少，因此以鸵鸟为主题的餐厅一定能满足人们的猎奇心理，是一种非常好的特色美食。', '<p class="正文" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 25pt;"><strong><span style="line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;">项目背景</span></strong></p><p class="正文" style="text-align:justify;margin-top:1.0pt;margin-bottom:1.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;"><span style="line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">有营养学专家预言，鸵鸟肉将是未来理想营养肉。虽然鸵鸟肉在国内并不为老百姓熟知，但在国际市场上却非常受欢迎，几乎到了供不应求的地步。有关资料显示1999年只有2%的意大利人知道鸵鸟肉，而今天意大利人要想吃到鸵鸟肉必须排队等候，鸵鸟肉将受到越来越高的礼遇，这已经是不争的事实。鸵鸟肉属纯红肌，具<span style="line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;"></span>有高蛋白，低脂肪，低胆固醇的特点，肌肉细嫩，口感鲜美，无异味，含有27种人类必须的氨基酸，易消化吸收，无药物残留，适合现代人养生的膳食潮流。鸵鸟肉作为烹饪原料具有广阔的发展前景。</span><br/></p><p class="正文" style="text-align:justify;margin-top:1.0pt;margin-bottom:1.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;"><span style="line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;"></span></p><p class="正文" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; line-height: 25pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;"></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"> &nbsp;项目优势</span></span></strong></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; line-height: 25pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"></span></span></strong></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 8pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;"></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">产品优势</span></strong></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 8pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 鸵鸟肉营养价值高，含有</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">27</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">种人类必须的氨基酸 ； 肉质细腻、口感鲜美，食用时不粘牙，没有丝毫腥味</span><span style="color:#333333;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;">，</span><span style="color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;">易消化</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">吸收，无药物残留；绿色健康食品， 鸵鸟肉的蛋白质含量为21</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">%</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">，脂肪含量低，脂肪含量仅为</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">2%</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">（牛肉为</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">17%</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">，猪肉为</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">19%</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">），胆固醇含量低，胆固醇含量为</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">62</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">毫克</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">/</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">百克（牛肉为</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">83</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">毫克，猪肉为</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">93</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">毫克）。</span></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 8pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">市场优势</span></strong></span></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 8pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 25pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 鸵鸟主题餐厅目前在大连尚属空白市场，拥有广阔的发展空间。如今海参鲍鱼已经不再让人觉得新奇，但像鸵鸟这种动物却是见过的人很多，吃过的人很少，因此以鸵鸟为主题的餐厅这种新鲜事物一定能满足人们的猎奇心理，是一种非常好的特色美食。</span></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 8pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 33.3333px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 该项目定位于中高端消费人群。大连是一座旅游城市，在东北地区为消费最高的城市之一，对餐饮行业非常有利，预计该项目实施后，年营业额可达300</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 33.3333px; text-align: justify;">万到500万。</span></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;"></span><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">供货渠道优势</span></strong></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 该项目已有了优质的鸵鸟肉、蛋的供货渠道，还可一并获得两百于道鸵鸟菜的制作方法。</span></p><p class="正文" style="margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; line-height: 25pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px;"></span></span></strong><br/></p><p class="正文" style="text-align:justify;margin-top:1.0pt;margin-bottom:1.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;宋体&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class="正文">&nbsp;</p><p class="正文" style="text-align:justify;margin-top:1.0pt;margin-bottom:1.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;"><span style="line-height: 25pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span><br/></p><p class="正文">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>', 60, 1000000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1493654739, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/59075661ae642.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 0, 0, 18, 245, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(468, 1, 39135, '汽车玻璃修复套装', '修复汽车玻璃的点状、星状裂痕。', '<p>&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px;color:white">汽车玻璃是两层的，开车路上行驶碰到石头或者其他情况导 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px;color:white">致玻璃产生点状、星状裂痕等在所难免。以往出现这种情况，面 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px;color:white">积大的只能跟换玻璃，国产车费用大概1000-2000元不等，进口 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px;color:white">车的玻璃跟换费用则上万，面积小的也要去修理店花上300、400 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px;color:white">元进行修复。本人经多年研究成果能快速修复上述裂痕，自己动 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px;color:white">手操作，简单易学，修旧如新，且大大降低了车主的维修费用。</span></p>', 30, 50000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1493700258, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/59080e2a6199b.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 0, 0, 14, 197, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(469, 1, 39135, '汽车玻璃修复套装', '修复汽车玻璃的点状、星状裂痕。', '<p style="text-align:center"><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px">汽车玻璃是两层的，开车路上行驶碰到石头或者其他情况导 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px">致玻璃产生点状、星状裂痕等在所难免。以往出现这种情况，面 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px">积大的只能跟换玻璃，国产车费用大概1000-2000元不等，进口 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px">车的玻璃跟换费用则上万，面积小的也要去修理店花上300、400 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px">元进行修复。本人经多年研究成果能快速修复上述裂痕，自己动 </span> <span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px">手操作，简单易学，修旧如新，且大大降低了车主的维修费用。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size:27px"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/59080f57e82ea.jpg" title="TB2fnTEjSJjpuFjy0FdXXXmoFXa_!!1677291602.jpg" alt="TB2fnTEjSJjpuFjy0FdXXXmoFXa_!!1677291602.jpg" width="716" height="447" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 716px; height: 447px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/59080f9e9fb13.jpg" title="TB2lB3zmpXXXXXaXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!2055587831.jpg" alt="TB2lB3zmpXXXXXaXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!2055587831.jpg" width="716" height="500" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 716px; height: 500px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/59080fe7a5b4f.jpg" title="TB2zBJtgl0lpuFjSszdXXcdxFXa_!!2367800387.jpg" alt="TB2zBJtgl0lpuFjSszdXXcdxFXa_!!2367800387.jpg" width="716" height="790" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 716px; height: 790px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/5908103fbc060.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 653px;" title="2.jpg" width="716" height="653" border="0" vspace="0" alt="2.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/5908103fd6edf.jpg" title="1.jpg" width="716" height="565" border="0" vspace="0" alt="1.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 565px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/59081040815e2.jpg" title="5.jpg" width="716" height="1354" border="0" vspace="0" alt="5.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 1354px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/590810409f2f3.jpg" title="3.jpg" width="716" height="1070" border="0" vspace="0" alt="3.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 1070px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/59081040ad9ce.jpg" title="4.jpg" width="716" height="544" border="0" vspace="0" alt="4.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 544px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/59081040c80f3.jpg" title="6.jpg" width="716" height="1351" border="0" vspace="0" alt="6.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 1351px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/5908114be385f.jpg" title="7.jpg" width="716" height="665" border="0" vspace="0" alt="7.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 665px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/5908114c0f7ce.jpg" title="8.jpg" width="716" height="1214" border="0" vspace="0" alt="8.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 1214px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/5908114c5d8cb.jpg" title="9.jpg" width="716" height="1120" border="0" vspace="0" alt="9.jpg" style="width: 716px; height: 1120px;"/></p><p><br/></p><p>&quot;</p><p>&quot;</p><p>&quot;</p>', 30, 30000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1493724708, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/59080ed49b97d.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 1, 0, 14, 197, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(470, 3, 39136, '良心农家自养生态猪', '让广大老百姓吃上无公害健康食品，让人们找回年味的感觉', '<p>小时候，你家杀过猪吗，你有和几个小伙伴一起吹起猪膀胱当球踢吗？那个年味的时代现在能找到吗？</p><p>据说几十年前，人们都不知道什么是“癌症”，可是现在人有很多不知不觉得了这个病那个病，得癌症的很多，原因就是病从口入，不是说人吃什么保健食品就能不生病的，而是在日常的生活中怎么样吃到健康无公害的食品，让健康从日常的吃饭开始，这也是广大人民群众的愿望。于是在河南南阳老家的大山里散养无公害无污染生态猪，面前已有100多头，主要喂菜，糠，玉米，平时猪都在山里吃野果子和橡树籽等，肉质鲜嫩，良心养殖。下一步会增加养殖无公害土鸡，羊，牛等，形成中原第一家生态无公害食品采购平台，让广大老百姓吃上无公害健康食品，让人们找回年味的感觉。</p>', 100, 200000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1493705304, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/59081ff3ce560.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 1, 0, 11, 156, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(471, 3, 39139, '大头菜', '四川的大头菜，。小的时候一到夏季，就见街坊邻居家家户户都晒大头菜，有用竹签穿着吊在屋檐口吹的，有放竹凉床上晒的，还有不见太阳阴在坛子里的然后洗好切好腌好封在倒扣的扑坛里，以水密封，越窖越香，经年不坏。', '<p>每家每户的工艺不尽相同，大头菜的口感也各有千秋。在过去食物匮乏的年代，一坛大头菜能支撑一个家庭渡过很长的时间。简简单单的一碟小咸菜，不作任何加工，就着稀饭馒头，脆生生的，让人唇齿生香，口留余味。</p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/590873af4856e.jpg" style="" title="2.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/590873af4bcb9.jpg" style="" title="3.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/590873af4da4a.jpg" style="" title="4.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/590873af78ff0.jpg" style="" title="5.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/590873af81613.jpg" style="" title="6.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170502/59087409538e8.jpg" title="7.jpg" alt="7.jpg"/></p>', 90, 5000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1493726221, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/59087250acd5c.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 1, 0, 26, 331, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(472, 8, 39144, '旅游酒店', '在河南新乡万仙山售票处建酒店，像我这个图片的酒店就是我们邻居建设的，年收益15W直接租出去的，先招募合伙人', '<p>我家宅基地就是河南新乡万仙山售票处门口，现家里的邻居都建起来酒店了，因自己家经济有限一下建不起来，找合伙人。</p><p>目前我知道的酒店年收益10W到15W之间，建设需要70W左右自己也出钱，剩余50W按照比例直接股份收益，</p><p>我们老家的都是建设好直接租出去的，年租金10到15万之间，保本收益，</p><p><br/></p>', 90, 500000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1494256356, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/59108977a09bb.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 1, 0, 11, 160, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 1, 0),
	(473, 4, 39161, '不一样的蓝牙耳机 享受智能通话音乐体验', '耳挂式S30蓝牙耳机采用按键与机头相结合，摆脱线控的种种弊端，让运动的激情根本停不下来', '<p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/591696669b7a9.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/59169668d03b9.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图2.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/59169668e015b.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图1.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/59169669028ac.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图3.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/59169669ecb93.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图4.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/5916966a99753.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图5.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/5916966ba15e4.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图5副本.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/5916966c64580.jpg" style="" title="光影魔术手拼图6.jpg"/></p><p><img src="http://www.zczyw.com/data/upload/ueditor/20170513/591696de5bfde.jpg" title="TB1hygAQpXXXXb6XXXXSutbFXXX.jpg" alt="TB1hygAQpXXXXb6XXXXSutbFXXX.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p>', 30, 5000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1494652646, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/5916959fb7633.jpg', '\' \'', '', 0, 1, 0, 6, 77, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(474, 4, 39168, '生态咖啡馆', '项目简介\r\n项目有三种行业：\r\n   1. 区域性众筹平台\r\n(众筹项目介绍)\r\n(区域众筹缺点与解决办法)\r\n2.生态造景\r\n3.咖啡馆', '<p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 35px"><span style="font-family:宋体">生态咖啡馆创业计划书</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一．项目简介</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">项目有三种行业：</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1. <span style="font-family:宋体">区域性众筹平台</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">(</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">众筹项目介绍</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">)</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">(</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">区域众筹缺点与解决办法</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">)</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">2.<span style="font-family:宋体">生态造景</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">3.<span style="font-family:宋体">咖啡馆</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">解决什么痛点</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">痛点一：如今微小型公司和个人有好的想法，没有办法搭建资金和人脉。就和我一样。这是痛点</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">找风投公司，找众筹平台，但是对于监管不方便，因此融资也不方便。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">解决办法：因此区域性众筹更能接地气带动微小型企业和个人良性的发展。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">痛点二：区域性众筹拓展全国各地区域是个难题</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">解决办法：</span> 1<span style="font-family:宋体">，与其他行业相互依存 ，比如生态造景行业，行业不同但是能互相依附。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span style="font-family:宋体">，用什么模式去扩展分店，</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体">在项目简介里的 发展计划有介绍</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">)</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.<span style="font-family:宋体">制作</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">APP</span><span style="font-family:宋体">并且推广</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">痛点三：环境恶劣，人们对于环境的要求越来越高</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">解决办法三：生态造景行业，是把大自然的一角搬入到室内。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:21px">二．</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">产品和运营</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">区域性众筹平台</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">众筹是如今国内探讨火热的词汇，筹钱，筹人，筹智，筹未来的精英圈子。众筹是非常适合项目的发展也能推进项目的成熟。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:Wingdings;font-size:19px"></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我们以咖啡馆为平台二次发展周边有梦想的消费人群为店铺新的股东，用他们的思维和人脉为店铺带来源源不断的客源和创新思维。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二次发展的股东带来的股金，在店铺运营平稳的情况下可以发展第二分店</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings;font-size: 19px">‚</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为周边有创业想法的青年发布众筹信息，优点是本地众筹股东也能给众筹的项目带来客源等，本店也为众筹项目的资金进行托管，收取一定佣金。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">(制作店铺APP，推广APP就是在推广店铺)</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我的众筹模式是以项目本地区域的人群为重点，开头难点绝对大，但是只要给与时间洗刷，绝对能做到火势燎原。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;line-height: 17px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">如今国内的众筹模式根本没有发挥绝对的优势，国内众筹平台针对的项目层面非常小，没有完美的把众筹所有的优势应用起来。</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">区域众筹才能更良性的带着项目发展，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">如果推广区域性众筹，更能把人，钱，资源完美的发挥，</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">我的项目就是为了迎合发展区域性众筹模式。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">打造区域性众筹平台与国内其他的众筹平台对接，可以把众筹模式完美起来。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">只有百分百的完美才能裂变，改变商业模式。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">区域性众筹平台的难点</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">：</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">区域性众筹拓展全国各地区域是个难题。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">我的解决办法：</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;1<span style="font-family:宋体">，与其他行业相互依存 </span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span style="font-family:宋体">，用什么模式去扩展分店，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">(</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">在下面发展计划里有介绍</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">)</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.制作APP并且推广</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;line-height: 17px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三．生态造景</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">国内算是新兴行业，而且国内环境恶劣，人们对于环境要求越来越高，也出现过高价卖空气的情况。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">所以个人考虑在别人没有反应过来之前成立公司抢占市场。生态造景是模拟大自然的气候，把气势宏伟，生机勃勃的自然一角搬入室内。产品有热带雨林缸，大型水草缸，植物壁挂，云雾林，沙漠造景，只要是自然的一角都可以开发成景观搬入室内。主营大型商务景观和小型家居景观。后期打造生态造景品牌设备。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">3咖啡馆</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">店内打造几个大型景观为特色，让消费者仿佛进入热带雨林的惬意。咖啡馆</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">也是另两种行业的平台</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:21px">三．</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发展计划</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">1.<span style="font-family:宋体">以咖啡馆为平台二次发展周边有梦想的消费人群为店铺新的股东，用他们的思维和人脉为店铺带来源源不断的客源和创新思维。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">二次发展的股东带来的股金，在店铺运营平稳的情况下可以发展第二分店</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">2.</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">以创业项目众筹为平台，发展有创业想法的人们利用他们的人脉众筹开分店。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">以省级市级第一家店为省级总店或市级总店，省级总店对下面分店有监督管理权，分店一部分利润进入总店作为管理费，所有分店都由总公司直营</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">。分店股东有监督提议权。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">每位众筹发起者可免费获得所筹店铺一部分股权</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">3.</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">制作公司</span>app <span style="font-family:宋体">。推广</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">APP</span><span style="font-family:宋体">就是推广店铺。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">APP<span style="font-family:宋体">页面，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">公司简介，公司店铺和正在筹备的分店显示，创业项目发布页面，二维码，店铺活动，股东与会员等级页面</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（股东所占店铺股份</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">职位级别</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">店铺每月效益</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">每月可得分红显示</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">或者是会员预存款显示），</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">每日好文等等</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">4.<span style="font-family:宋体">在店铺经营平稳情况下发展生态造景品牌 。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:21px">四．</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公司的宗旨</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">为创业者搭建资金与人脉</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">2<span style="font-family:宋体">为推广绿化添砖加瓦</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">3<span style="font-family:宋体">为那些城市中疲劳的人们</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">打造惬意的环境重燃激情的平台</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">五．融资计划</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">店铺房租</span>20<span style="font-family:宋体">万</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">店铺装修</span>20<span style="font-family:宋体">万</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">店铺造景</span>15<span style="font-family:宋体">万</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公司运行</span>50<span style="font-family:宋体">万</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公司需要筹集启动资金</span>105<span style="font-family:宋体">万</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">六．公司成员</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">创始人：姚玉修</span> &nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">掌舵公司的方向，负责公司的运营</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">因为我接触有限，项目怎么操作对接人群，宣传推广，销售等等我有太多的不足，周边的人群也给不了我太多的建议。我找投资人，不但是要他的钱，还要他的思维模式，和团队能力。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">造景师</span>:<span style="font-family:宋体">因为生态造景圈子不大，国内比较有名的造景师我认识几个，所以找全职和兼职的造景师不难。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">店长，</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">服务员，</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">宣传</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财务</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">等只能在店铺运营初期再找了，也会找二次股东兼职。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:21px">八．</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">生态造景视频</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">雨林</span></p><p><a href="http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ2OTg4OTA3Mg==.html?x&sharefrom=android"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);font-size: 13px">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ2OTg4OTA3Mg==.html?x&amp;sharefrom=android</span></span></a><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:13px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">水草</span></p><p><a href="http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNzI4Mzg5MDA0.html"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);font-size: 16px">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNzI4Mzg5MDA0.html</span></span></a></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">雨林造景</span></p><p><a href="http://m.youku.com/video/id_XMTQyOTkyNTg1Mg==.html?x=&sharefrom=android&from=timeline"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);font-size: 16px">http://m.youku.com/video/id_XMTQyOTkyNTg1Mg==.html?x=&amp;sharefrom=android&amp;from=timeline</span></span></a></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">九．联系方式</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style