宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">2．</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">团队全职人数及创始人完整介绍？</span> </span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">团队如今只有我个人</span> &nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">个人介绍如上</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">3．</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">整体市场规模有多大？</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">个人认为众筹能改变国内的商业模式，但是市场规模我无法提供数据</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;line-height: 17px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', 90, 1000000.00, 0, 0, 0.00, 1494861270, 0, 0, '/data/upload/201705/5919c5d1c94f2.jpg', '\' \'', 'http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ2OTg4OTA3Mg==.html?x&amp;sharefrom=android     ', 0, 0, 0, 22, 284, ' ', ' ', ' ', 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(475, 4, 39168, '生态咖啡馆', '项目简介项目有三种行业：  \r\n 1. 区域性众筹平台\r\n(众筹项目介绍)(区域众筹缺点与解决办法)\r\n2.生态造景\r\n3.咖啡馆 ', '<p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 35px"><span style="font-family:宋体">生态咖啡馆创业计划书</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一．项目简介</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">项目有三种行业：</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1. <span style="font-family:宋体">区域性众筹平台</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">(</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">众筹项目介绍</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">)</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">(</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">区域众筹缺点与解决办法</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">)</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">2.<span style="font-family:宋体">生态造景</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">3.<span style="font-family:宋体">咖啡馆</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">解决什么痛点</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">痛点一：如今微小型公司和个人有好的想法，没有办法搭建资金和人脉。就和我一样。这是痛点</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">找风投公司，找众筹平台，但是对于监管不方便，因此融资也不方便。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">解决办法：因此区域性众筹更能接地气带动微小型企业和个人良性的发展。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">痛点二：区域性众筹拓展全国各地区域是个难题</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">解决办法：</span> 1<span style="font-family:宋体">，与其他行业相互依存 ，比如生态造景行业，行业不同但是能互相依附。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span style="font-family:宋体">，用什么模式去扩展分店，</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体">在项目简介里的 发展计划有介绍</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">)</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.<span style="font-family:宋体">制作</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">APP</span><span style="font-family:宋体">并且推广</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">痛点三：环境恶劣，人们对于环境的要求越来越高</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">解决办法三：生态造景行业，是把大自然的一角搬入到室内。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:21px">二．</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">产品和运营</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">1区域性众筹平台</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">众筹是如今国内探讨火热的词汇，筹钱，筹人，筹智，筹未来的精英圈子。众筹是非常适合项目的发展也能推进项目的成熟。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:Wingdings;font-size:19px"></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我们以咖啡馆为平台二次发展周边有梦想的消费人群为店铺新的股东，用他们的思维和人脉为店铺带来源源不断的客源和创新思维。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二次发展的股东带来的股金，在店铺运营平稳的情况下可以发展第二分店</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: Wingdings;font-size: 19px">‚</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为周边有创业想法的青年发布众筹信息，优点是本地众筹股东也能给众筹的项目带来客源等，本店也为众筹项目的资金进行托管，收取一定佣金。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">(制作店铺APP，推广APP就是在推广店铺)</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我的众筹模式是以项目本地区域的人群为重点，开头难点绝对大，但是只要给与时间洗刷，绝对能做到火势燎原。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;line-height: 17px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">如今国内的众筹模式根本没有发挥绝对的优势，国内众筹平台针对的项目层面非常小，没有完美的把众筹所有的优势应用起来。</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">区域众筹才能更良性的带着项目发展，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">如果推广区域性众筹，更能把人，钱，资源完美的发挥，</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">我的项目就是为了迎合发展区域性众筹模式。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">打造区域性众筹平台与国内其他的众筹平台对接，可以把众筹模式完美起来。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">只有百分百的完美才能裂变，改变商业模式。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">区域性众筹平台的难点</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">：</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">区域性众筹拓展全国各地区域是个难题。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">我的解决办法：</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;1<span style="font-family:宋体">，与其他行业相互依存 </span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span style="font-family:宋体">，用什么模式去扩展分店，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">(</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">在下面发展计划里有介绍</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">)</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.制作APP并且推广</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;line-height: 17px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">2．生态造景</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">国内算是新兴行业，而且国内环境恶劣，人们对于环境要求越来越高，也出现过高价卖空气的情况。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">所以个人考虑在别人没有反应过来之前成立公司抢占市场。生态造景是模拟大自然的气候，把气势宏伟，生机勃勃的自然一角搬入室内。产品有热带雨林缸，大型水草缸，植物壁挂，云雾林，沙漠造景，只要是自然的一角都可以开发成景观搬入室内。主营大型商务景观和小型家居景观。后期打造生态造景品牌设备。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">3咖啡馆</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">店内打造几个大型景观为特色，让消费者仿佛进入热带雨林的惬意。咖啡馆</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">也是另两种行业的平台</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:21px">三．</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发展计划</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">1.<span style="font-family:宋体">以咖啡馆为平台二次发展周边有梦想的消费人群为店铺新的股东，用他们的思维和人脉为店铺带来源源不断的客源和创新思维。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">二次发展的股东带来的股金，在店铺运营平稳的情况下可以发展第二分店</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">2.</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">以创业项目众筹为平台，发展有创业想法的人们利用他们的人脉众筹开分店。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">以省级市级第一家店为省级总店或市级总店，省级总店对下面分店有监督管理权，分店一部分利润进入总店作为管理费，所有分店都由总公司直营</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">。分店股东有监督提议权。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">每位众筹发起者可免费获得所筹店铺一部分股权</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">3.</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">制作公司</span>app <span style="font-family:宋体">。推广</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">APP</span><span style="font-family:宋体">就是推广店铺。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">APP<span style="font-family:宋体">页面，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">公司简介，公司店铺和正在筹备的分店显示，创业项目发布页面，二维码，店铺活动，股东与会员等级页面</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（股东所占店铺股份</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">职位级别</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">店铺每月效益</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">每月可得分红显示</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">或者是会员预存款显示），</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">每日好文等等</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">4.<span style="font-family:宋体">在店铺经营平稳情况下发展生态造景品牌 。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:21px">四．</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公司的宗旨</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: